---
layout: base.njk
title: News & Updates
description: Updates on RiP education efforts, community partnerships, seasonal reminders, and Great Lakes water safety information.
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <p class="eyebrow">News & Updates</p>
    <h1>Community updates, education work, and seasonal safety reminders.</h1>
    <p class="lead">RiP shares updates to keep our community informed, engaged, and prepared throughout the year.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      {% set posts = collections.news | reverse %}
      {% for post in posts %}
        {% include "post-card.njk" %}
      {% else %}
        <article class="card">
          <h2>No posts yet</h2>
          <p>Check back for updates about school visits, community events, and seasonal safety reminders.</p>
        </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-muted">
  <div class="container grid grid-3">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>School Visits & Education Programs</h2>
      <p>RiP regularly visits schools to deliver age-appropriate water safety education focused on rip current awareness and informed decision-making.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Community Events & Outreach</h2>
      <p>Community events, workshops, beach safety days, and municipal partnerships strengthen shared understanding and responsibility for water safety.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Seasonal Safety Reminders</h2>
      <p>Clear, timely information helps people make safer choices during spring hazards, summer beach use, and fall shoulder-season conditions.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
